 $A$\nand $A^{op}$ are $\\kappa$-frames), and use this to prove a general $\\kappa$-ary\ninterpolation theorem for $(\\kappa, \\kappa)$-frames, which dualizes to the\naforementioned separation theorems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Nov 2020 06:19:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
